s nasal breathing turns rough, it\u2019s a sure sign that it is becoming angry. However, because it goes into a towering rage almost instantly, it is impossible for anyone to flee its wrath."},{"version":"emerald","text":"When it starts shaking and its nasal breathing turns rough, it\u2019s a sure sign of anger. However, since this happens instantly, there is no time to flee."},{"version":"firered","text":"Light and agile on its feet, and ferocious in temperament. When angered, it flies into an uncontrollable frenzy."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"Extremely quick to anger. It could be docile one moment, then thrashing away  the next instant."},{"version":"diamond","text":"It lives in treetop colonies. If one becomes enraged, the whole colony rampages for no reason."},{"version":"pearl","text":"It lives in treetop colonies. If one becomes enraged, the whole colony rampages for no reason."},{"version":"platinum","text":"It lives in treetop colonies. If one becomes enraged, the whole colony rampages for no reason."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"It is extremely ill-tempered. Groups of them will attack any handy target for no reason."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"It\u2019s unsafe to approach if it gets violently enraged for no reason and can\u2019t distinguish friends from foes."},{"version":"black","text":"It lives in treetop colonies. If one becomes enraged, the whole colony rampages for no reason."},{"version":"white","text":"It lives in treetop colonies. If one becomes enraged, the whole colony rampages for no reason."},{"version":"black-2","text":"It lives in treetop colonies. If one becomes enraged, the whole colony rampages for no reason."},{"version":"white-2","text":"It lives in treetop colonies. If one becomes enraged, the whole colony rampages for no reason."},{"version":"x","text":"It\u2019s unsafe to approach if it gets violently enraged for no reason and can\u2019t distinguish friends from foes."},{"version":"y","text":"It lives in treetop colonies. If one becomes enraged, the whole colony rampages for no reason."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"When Mankey starts shaking and its nasal breathing turns rough, it\u2019s a sure sign that it is becoming angry. However, because it goes into a towering rage almost instantly, it is impossible for anyone to flee its wrath."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"When Mankey starts shaking and its nasal breathing turns rough, it\u2019s a sure sign that it is becoming angry. However, because it goes into a towering rage almost instantly, it is impossible for anyone to flee its wrath."},{"version":"sun","text":"It can spontaneously become enraged. Everyone near it clears out as it rampages, and the resulting loneliness makes it angrier still."},{"version":"moon","text":"Its raging tires it out and causes it to fall asleep, but the anger resonating in its dreams causes it to wake up\u2014which infuriates it all over again."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"The smallest of things could cause it to lose its temper. Because it doesn\u2019t hold in its stress, this Pok\u00e9mon can live a long time."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"If one gets angry, all the others around it will get angry, so silence is a rare visitor in a troop of Mankey."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"An agile Pok\u00e9mon that lives in trees. It angers easily and will not hesitate to attack anything."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"An agile Pok\u00e9mon that lives in trees. It angers easily and will not hesitate to attack anything."}],"evo":{"name":"mankey","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"primeape","level":1,"min_level":28,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":nu